			Increases damage by 50% and 100% chance to inflict shadow flame
			Bow mode : Arrow are imbues with special curse that constantly spawn dark wisp for 1s.
			Gun mode : Shoot arch of 4 smaller dark bolt deal 150% of weapon damage.

			Wait additional 1s to releases dark wave dealing 200% weapon damage which completely ignore defense

			On switching to other weapon after dealing 34000 damage, you shoot dark bolt and spawn dark wisp for 6s
